subject: Last two files I posted....
author: Adriana Jones
full_text: .... are related, in my mind... one thing I listen for is repetitions over time,because I feel that gives me clues as to what the heck might be going on it that box... in this case I believe I heard someone on two different occasions (January 4 and March 17) address apparently a demon (?????) and tell them to "drop him"..... this sounds scary and negative and I don't like it, but I can't help this is what I got... anyone else here it like I did?
